Judul: CUSTOMER PROFILE IN RELATION TO FUNDING COMPOSITION AT BANK X (CASE STUDY: BANK X WEST JAVA REGIONAL OFFICE)
Abstrak: In this research, there are key factors that are used which are funding, liquidity, and risk. The analysis will be using proportional test in order to find the percentage of some factors in contributing the funding composition. The data analyses will also use Binary Logit Regression Model analysis in order to dertermine what kinds of customer profile such as type of currency, religion, range of ages, jobs, and time to maturity that is influencing the most to funding composition at Bank X West Java Regional Area.
